data.description: Impeccable, Move-In Ready Home in Desirable Oaknoll. Situated on a 0.52 acr lot that backs up to mature trees and offers a lot of privacy. 3 Bdr, 2.5 Baths, basement, 2-car garage, fenced-in yard with space galore for a back yard play. Spacious master suite has a large walk-in closet, great room with a cathedral ceiling; kitchen and bathrooms have been renovated and styled to please; there are new carpet, tiled floor, & neutral dcor. A Must See! $219,900.  Call Victoria Hudgins to schedule a tour: 302-359-2911 Cell.
